com.interpss.core.sparse.solver.csj

Interface ICSJSparseEqnSolver

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ISparseEqnSolver
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseCSJEqnComplexSolver, BaseCSJEqnDoubleSolver, BaseCSJSparseEqnSolver, CSJLeastSquareDoubleSolver, CSJSqaureMatrixEqnDoubleSolver, CSJSquareMatrixEqnComplexSolver, CSJWeightedLeastSquareDoubleSolver, SparseEqnComplexSolver, SparseEqnDoubleSolver

    public interface ICSJSparseEqnSolver
extends ISparseEqnSolver
    CSJ Sparse Equation of data type double for solving the [A]X=B problem. [A] could be a non-square matrix. The solution process in general includes 1) factorization; 2) solving the equation. To outside, the index number is from 0 to n-1.
